1
00:00:40,150 --> 00:00:43,440
♪I don't want to hear you
nagging nonstop♪

2
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,790
♪Can't you just give me the result♪

3
00:00:47,100 --> 00:00:49,960
♪Don't think being older
makes you so much greater♪

4
00:00:50,170 --> 00:00:51,710
♪Just bring it on♪

5
00:00:51,910 --> 00:00:53,170
♪Watch how I'll handle you♪

6
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,080
♪Hey, I'll just keep on nagging♪

7
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:59,010
♪Keep on nagging♪

8
00:00:59,010 --> 00:01:02,030
♪You're annoying; do not get me mad♪

9
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:05,140
♪I'm always the one
taking the blame for you♪

10
00:01:05,140 --> 00:01:08,690
♪Don't be afraid to speak;
I might hold a grudge♪

11
00:01:08,690 --> 00:01:09,970
♪No. 132♪

12
00:01:09,970 --> 00:01:10,910
♪357, what do you want♪

13
00:01:11,110 --> 00:01:12,280
♪Stop right there♪

14
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:16,900
♪In this noisy, rowdy world,
fate is so amazing♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:20,150
♪When we go crazy together,
joy is always with us♪

16
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:23,260
♪We'll party till dawn♪

17
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:26,540
♪Laughing, jumping, with no worries♪

18
00:01:26,540 --> 00:01:28,060
♪You're clearly so strange♪

19
00:01:28,060 --> 00:01:29,580
♪I'm clearly so cute♪

20
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:32,630
♪Even if they don't get it,
it doesn't matter♪

21
00:01:32,630 --> 00:01:36,330
♪Even if it's always crazy and weird♪

22
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:39,410
♪I still need fresh reasons for myself♪

23
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:47,070
=Hilarious Family 2=

24
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:50,260
=Episode 7=

25
00:01:57,770 --> 00:01:58,690
Kan.

26
00:01:58,690 --> 00:01:59,920
This place is a bit remote.

27
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:01,640
You don't understand.

28
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:03,310
Masters like them

29
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:05,320
basically live in places like this.

30
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:10,360
Where is it?

31
00:02:16,130 --> 00:02:17,070
Is anyone here?

32
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:18,920
Where are your manners?

33
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:37,110
Tea Master, nice to meet you.

34
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:38,950
I came unannounced.

35
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,410
The door wasn't properly closed.

36
00:02:41,410 --> 00:02:42,350
So...

37
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:49,040
Thank you.

38
00:02:56,850 --> 00:02:57,920
When boiling water,

39
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:01,640
if bubbles appear like shrimp eyes,

40
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:04,760
the water is boiling but not overcooked.

41
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:07,480
Cai Junmo believes

42
00:03:07,890 --> 00:03:11,880
overcooked water
isn't fit for brewing tea.

43
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,830
As expected of the Tea Master.

44
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:16,320
You're clearly an expert.

45
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,830
I feel he's a bit pretentious.

46
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:20,270
Masters are like that.

47
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:26,550
Put down Tao Baowen.

48
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:30,640
That's the teacup you took.

49
00:03:31,290 --> 00:03:33,880
If you break it,
you can't afford to compensate.

50
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:37,360
This even has a name?

51
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:39,010
The Song people named

52
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:40,380
twelve tea utensils

53
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:41,390
based on official titles,

54
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:43,480
so they are called the 12 Courtiers.

55
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:46,080
The one you took is Tao Baowen.

56
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:49,190
Kan, can you understand this?

57
00:03:51,890 --> 00:03:52,890
Tea Master,

58
00:03:52,890 --> 00:03:54,010
I came unannounced today

59
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:54,990
because I have a request.

60
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,920
Meeting is fate.

61
00:03:59,610 --> 00:04:01,320
Since you came
while I was boiling water,

62
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,760
you're my guest.

63
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:05,060
When it comes to whisking tea,

64
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:06,360
though the techniques differ,

65
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:07,950
the principles are the same.

66
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:09,880
If the stirring is weak

67
00:04:10,690 --> 00:04:12,230
or the amount of water is insufficient,

68
00:04:12,570 --> 00:04:15,270
the tea won't mix properly,
and the fragrance disperses.

69
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,560
If the water is too much

70
00:04:17,730 --> 00:04:19,220
or the wrist movement is not rounded,

71
00:04:19,250 --> 00:04:22,470
the tea's strength is lost,
and froth forms easily.

72
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,240
Tea has true fragrance,

73
00:04:26,610 --> 00:04:28,760
but it must be steamed and pressed,

74
00:04:29,170 --> 00:04:30,830
dried and ground,

75
00:04:31,410 --> 00:04:32,880
and ground finely and whisked.

76
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:35,350
Only then can its clear aroma spread,

77
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:38,350
and its harmony and beauty be complete.

78
00:04:41,410 --> 00:04:42,350
Thank you.

79
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:47,840
Taste it.

80
00:05:02,730 --> 00:05:03,660
How is it?

81
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:04,680
This tea is indeed

82
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,600
quite ordinary.

83
00:05:10,410 --> 00:05:11,350
Let me try.

84
00:05:22,410 --> 00:05:23,250
It's drinkable.

85
00:05:23,250 --> 00:05:24,190
Right?

86
00:05:26,410 --> 00:05:27,350
Tea Master,

87
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:29,080
we are not saying your tea is bad.

88
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:30,930
But we are not very familiar

89
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:31,880
with whisking tea.

90
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:33,470
Usually, the tea we drink

91
00:05:33,470 --> 00:05:35,220
is brewed.

92
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,280
Yes.

93
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:38,440
You're forgetting the tradition.

94
00:05:39,410 --> 00:05:41,950
Though brewing is convenient,

95
00:05:42,730 --> 00:05:43,670
does it have

96
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,800
any aesthetic value?

97
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,560
Tea whisking

98
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:49,950
is traditional

99
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:51,560
and has a deep history.

100
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,580
Even people from Ryukyu

101
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:54,680
study our method.

102
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:55,980
How can we

103
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,710
forget it so easily?

104
00:05:58,730 --> 00:05:59,710
You are right.

105
00:06:00,050 --> 00:06:01,300
We can't forget our tradition.

106
00:06:02,020 --> 00:06:03,660
But not everyone has the conditions

107
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:04,510
to sit down quietly

108
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,680
and whisk a cup of tea.

109
00:06:06,170 --> 00:06:08,000
I think if tea is to develop well,

110
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:09,140
more people need

111
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:10,200
to experience its quality

112
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,680
in a simpler way.

113
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,910
It seems you know quite a lot

114
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:17,150
about tea.

115
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:18,840
Tea Master, here's the thing.

116
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,000
May I ask if you have

117
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:21,410
any of the finest

118
00:06:21,410 --> 00:06:23,080
pan-fired tea?

119
00:06:23,610 --> 00:06:24,550
Why?

120
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,780
We want to get a batch

121
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:27,800
to sell in our shop.

122
00:06:29,730 --> 00:06:30,670
No.

123
00:06:31,490 --> 00:06:33,020
Actually, we...

124
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:33,960
I don't have any.

125
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:42,080
Sorry to trouble you.

126
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:44,560
Guiwei, let's go.

127
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:45,790
Kan...

128
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:49,000
You didn't even respect Jinyu Tea,

129
00:06:49,410 --> 00:06:50,590
and you're the Tea Master?

130
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:52,120
Don't say that.

131
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:53,840
Wait.

132
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:58,560
You are from Jinyu Tea?

133
00:06:58,810 --> 00:06:59,750
Yes.

134
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:03,350
Jinyu Tea

135
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:05,120
is famous for pan-fired tea.

136
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:07,240
Actually, pan-firing has existed

137
00:07:07,490 --> 00:07:08,470
since ancient times,

138
00:07:09,170 --> 00:07:11,250
but it was popularized

139
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,610
by Monk Da Fang,

140
00:07:12,610 --> 00:07:13,590
who made Songluo Tea.

141
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:15,780
I've heard of him.

142
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:16,920
My mother told me about him.

143
00:07:17,490 --> 00:07:19,350
I have five jin of the finest bud tea.

144
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,300
It is pan-fired using the secret method

145
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:23,600
of Monk Da Fang's Songluo Tea.

146
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,640
I wonder

147
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,120
if you are interested.

148
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:28,720
Of course.

149
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:30,440
Then I will reluctantly

150
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:32,000
sell some to you.

151
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,270
Kan, do we want it?

152
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:36,000
Actually, I have some connection

153
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:37,800
with Jinyu Tea.

154
00:07:39,220 --> 00:07:40,810
Consider it my way of repaying a favor.

155
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:42,520
Repaying a favor?

156
00:07:42,780 --> 00:07:43,700
Don't ask.

157
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:44,640
Guiwei, don't ask.

158
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:46,490
Everyone has some

159
00:07:46,490 --> 00:07:47,760
unpleasant past.

160
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:49,430
We respect that.

161
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,730
We respect that.

162
00:07:50,730 --> 00:07:51,780
Kan, I didn't want to ask.

163
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:52,720
Even if you did,

164
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:55,380
I wouldn't tell.

165
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:01,460
But I have two conditions.

166
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,100
First,

167
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:04,300
if you don't sell it

168
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:05,780
within three days,

169
00:08:05,780 --> 00:08:07,300
I will take the tea back.

170
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:08,860
Second,

171
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:10,580
pay first.

172
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:12,780
Kan,

173
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,460
100 taels for five jin of tea,

174
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:16,220
and it must be paid first.

175
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,540
You agreed so easily?

176
00:08:18,130 --> 00:08:18,930
It seems Tea Master

177
00:08:18,930 --> 00:08:19,880
doesn't quite understand

178
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:21,180
his influence in the tea world.

179
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:22,740
What do you mean?

180
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:25,300
I don't just want the Songluo Tea

181
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:26,740
but also his reputation.

182
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:29,460
Beiju Master, Nan Master, and he

183
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,020
are top figures in the tea world.

184
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:32,480
People would pay 200 taels

185
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:33,820
for the five jin of tea,

186
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:40,180
let alone just 100 taels.

187
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:41,260
Really?

188
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:43,740
I want to shock those

189
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:45,300
who look down on me.

190
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:46,700
Alright, Kan.

191
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:48,260
Good that you're confident.

192
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:50,180
I also realized
you really know a lot about tea.

193
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:53,180
I've been influenced since childhood.

194
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:54,340
I will study seriously.

195
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,500
I won't let you

196
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,420
and my cousin down.

197
00:08:56,780 --> 00:08:57,700
Trust me.

198
00:08:58,900 --> 00:08:59,820
Guiwei,

199
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:01,500
I'm really relieved by this.

200
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:03,540
Do you have 100 taels of silver?

201
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:11,300
Hurry, we need it now.

202
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,080
I'm afraid he will regret it.

203
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,820
We must finalize this deal first.

204
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,900
So, you don't have money?

205
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:19,340
After this deal is done,

206
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,020
I'll give you 150 taels.

207
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,300
No, it's not about 150 taels.

208
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,300
You now...

209
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:27,020
You are the shop manager.

210
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,180
We need to work together

211
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,900
to make it big and strong, right?

212
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:32,820
Besides,

213
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:34,060
I've already said it.

214
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,660
If my shop fails in three months,

215
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,700
it will close.

216
00:09:38,180 --> 00:09:39,580
Will you still be able to manage it?

217
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:40,660
Can I pay back the money

218
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:41,580
I owe your cousin?

219
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:43,700
What can we do then?

220
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:45,620
Sell fish like that kid?

221
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:46,540
I won't sell fish.

222
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:50,020
I only have a few taels of silver.

223
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,300
But my cousin's money is with me.

224
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:56,000
How much does your cousin have?

225
00:09:57,700 --> 00:09:58,900
It should be enough.

226
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:05,100
Every time I needed help the most,

227
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,940
it was Sixi who helped me.

228
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:12,260
Thinking about it, I really miss her.

229
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,620
Run?

230
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:15,940
You wanted to run?

231
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,540
Now, you know better?

232
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:20,060
When you go out,

233
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,860
will you uphold a wife's duty,

234
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:24,020
respect your husband,
and be grateful to your in-laws?

235
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:26,180
Move.

236
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,900
Why is he here?

237
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:31,100
He's even at the door.

238
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,420
Sixi.

239
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:35,700
Sixi?

240
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:36,980
Here!

241
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:42,740
Quiet!

242
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:44,540
Sixi.

243
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,180
Sixi.

244
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,180
Mr. Jing.

245
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:50,540
Here.

246
00:10:55,420 --> 00:10:56,340
Well.

247
00:10:57,380 --> 00:10:58,300
What's that sound?

248
00:10:58,380 --> 00:10:59,540
Someone is slaughtering a sow.

249
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:01,300
We'll eat pork knuckles for lunch.

250
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:02,420
Pork knuckles for lunch?

251
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:03,460
Why not join us?

252
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:04,380
I'll pass.

253
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,140
I just want to see Sixi.

254
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,420
Bad timing.

255
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:09,020
Sixi went to arrange flowers.

256
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:09,940
Why not join us?

257
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:11,780
No need.

258
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,660
Is she doing well?

259
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,540
She's eating well,

260
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:16,940
gaining some weight.

261
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,020
That's good.

262
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:20,200
By the way, I brought Sixi

263
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,320
her favorite lotus pastries

264
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,660
and lotus root pudding.

265
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,420
Please give them to her.

266
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:26,820
- Okay.
- This is for you.

267
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,900
A little gesture.

268
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,220
I have some, too?

269
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:30,320
Please take it.

270
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:31,620
You are too kind.

271
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:32,540
Mr. Jing.

272
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,620
By the way,

273
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,500
there's one more thing

274
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,460
to tell Sixi.

275
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:37,380
Well.

276
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:41,020
I borrowed the 100 taels

277
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:41,940
she left with Guiwei.

278
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:44,300
You're being silly.

279
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:46,180
Her money is your money.

280
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,420
Just use it.

281
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,380
How sensible of you.

282
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:50,860
Quiet.

283
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:52,140
Shut up!

284
00:11:52,140 --> 00:11:53,820
Quiet.

285
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,140
Is that the sound of a sow?

286
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,340
A wild boar.

287
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:59,220
A wild boar?

288
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,180
No wonder it sounds so lively.

289
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,620
Then I won't disturb you.

290
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:04,860
I'll take my leave.

291
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:05,980
Take care.

292
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,900
Pork for lunch.

293
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,100
How nice.

294
00:12:10,580 --> 00:12:11,820
Take care, Young Master.

295
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:12,940
Alright.

296
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,260
You want to call, huh?

297
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:17,820
You want to call?

298
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:20,100
Let her shout.

299
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:22,140
He's already far away.

300
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:25,860
Desperate?

301
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:28,460
The one you love was at the door,

302
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,860
but you couldn't see him.

303
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:35,660
What did you say?

304
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,660
I said

305
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:39,980
he couldn't use the money.

306
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:43,180
You haven't learned anything at all.

307
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,620
You're married to him.

308
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,900
Forget about the money.

309
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:49,100
I want...

310
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:51,260
You want what?

311
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:53,380
I want to bite you.

312
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,660
Hold on, Zhu.

313
00:12:58,060 --> 00:12:59,140
Stop it!

314
00:13:06,060 --> 00:13:07,980
You, little brat.

315
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,060
How dare you bite me?

316
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:14,180
(Jinyu Tea)

317
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,340
Why hasn't Tea Master's tea

318
00:13:16,340 --> 00:13:17,460
arrived yet?

319
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:19,180
Kan.

320
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:20,700
Kan, something's wrong.

321
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:22,420
What happened?

322
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:23,340
The tea...

323
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,740
I went to the Tea Master's courtyard
to urge the tea,

324
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:26,660
but

325
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:28,060
it was empty.

326
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:28,900
What?

327
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:29,820
I...

328
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:34,500
Kan, hurry.

329
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:36,900
There's nothing left.

330
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,580
The Tea Master

331
00:13:39,580 --> 00:13:40,600
turns out to be a fraud.

332
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:43,460
Kan, do you think

333
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:45,340
he was the true Tea Master?

334
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:49,100
Not good.

335
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:50,500
We've been scammed.

336
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:51,860
Guiwei,

337
00:13:51,860 --> 00:13:53,060
look around and see

338
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,660
if we can find this fake Tea Master.

339
00:13:55,300 --> 00:13:56,680
I'll go find that fish-selling kid.

340
00:13:57,420 --> 00:13:58,540
The fish-selling trickster.

341
00:13:58,540 --> 00:13:59,940
See, you're so anxious.

342
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:01,500
Go.

343
00:14:05,140 --> 00:14:06,060
Fish boy.

344
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:16,700
He even believed a kid.

345
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:19,140
He's so gullible.

346
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:21,060
I knew long ago
that the Tea Master was a fraud,

347
00:14:21,060 --> 00:14:22,740
so I used it.

348
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,700
Do you know what this trick is called?

349
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,340
It's called the trick of a kid.

350
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:31,580
Who's he?

351
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:33,380
He's the kid.

352
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:34,660
I mean,

353
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:36,580
why are you laughing here?

354
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:38,940
Without me, could you have done this?

355
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:40,180
Yes, yes.

356
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:41,540
Liu,

357
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:43,140
did you do the thing

358
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:44,140
you promised me?

359
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:45,700
Don't worry.

360
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:47,300
We've avenged your sister.

361
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:49,340
Ai Sixi, who fooled your sister,

362
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:50,780
has been sent to Yuanyang House.

363
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:52,540
Cuiying arranged for someone

364
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:53,380
to take care of her.

365
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:55,540
Now, she's probably dying.

366
00:14:56,460 --> 00:14:57,460
Let's have a drink.

367
00:14:57,980 --> 00:14:59,340
- Cheers.
- What did you say?

368
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:01,140
What happened to Sixi?

369
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:02,060
This...

370
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:04,900
I'm just a kid.

371
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:06,580
They made me do it.

372
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:07,860
Mother!

373
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,780
(Yuanyang House)
Discipline yourselves.

374
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,860
Pay attention to your words.

375
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:19,820
Sixi.

376
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,740
Who are you?

377
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:23,620
Sixi.

378
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:28,940
Breathe.

379
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:31,220
So hot.

380
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:32,420
It's gone.

381
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:36,380
All my money is gone.

382
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:37,380
Still alive.

383
00:15:37,380 --> 00:15:38,300
Not dead yet.

384
00:15:39,020 --> 00:15:40,140
Not dead.

385
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:41,660
She scared me to death.

386
00:15:42,420 --> 00:15:43,340
Sixi.

387
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:48,820
Mr. Jing.

388
00:15:54,940 --> 00:15:56,660
Sixi, Sixi.

389
00:15:58,340 --> 00:15:59,260
Untie her!

390
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,900
- Okay.
- I can leave?

391
00:16:00,900 --> 00:16:01,860
I can leave?

392
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:04,500
Sixi.

393
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:05,860
So thirsty.

394
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:08,140
- I'll take you out.
- I want water.

395
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:11,180
- I want water.
- Sixi.

396
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:15,820
Jing Kan.

397
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:17,220
Sixi.

398
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:22,580
Give me back my money.

399
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:24,300
Money? Not now.

400
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:29,660
Just wait.

401
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,760
I won't talk back
when my husband curses me.

402
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:44,620
I won't fight back
when his parents hit me.

403
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:46,860
I won't talk back...

404
00:16:47,420 --> 00:16:48,700
I'll fight you!

405
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:51,420
Sixi,

406
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,540
you're awake.

407
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:55,580
Guiwei.

408
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:59,460
There really is hell in this world,

409
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:01,820
and it's just two streets away.

410
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:07,060
Sixi, are you feeling better?

411
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:12,620
Where's my money?

412
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:15,900
Tell me.

413
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:17,060
Sixi.

414
00:17:18,020 --> 00:17:18,940
Sixi.

415
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,280
Don't worry.

416
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,220
I already sent someone

417
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,560
to deliver the approval documents

418
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:23,300
from Grandmother.

419
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,100
Rest well at home.

420
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:25,020
No one will hurt you.

421
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:26,300
Don't think about anything else.

422
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:27,220
Don't overthink.

423
00:17:28,740 --> 00:17:29,660
Sixi, what do you need?

424
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,020
I need to leave here immediately.

425
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:36,700
Get up first.

426
00:17:37,980 --> 00:17:38,700
Sixi.

427
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:39,940
I didn't expect that Luo Zhusi

428
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:41,660
had arranged things in Yuanyang House.

429
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:42,940
Don't worry.

430
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:44,420
I will not spare her.

431
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:46,140
Please spare me first.

432
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:47,060
I beg you.

433
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:49,540
Guiwei,

434
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:50,900
give me back my money.

435
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:54,820
Sixi,

436
00:17:55,580 --> 00:17:56,620
we were scammed.

437
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:57,980
The money's gone.

438
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:01,220
All gone?

439
00:18:03,140 --> 00:18:05,020
Sixi, sit for a moment.

440
00:18:10,140 --> 00:18:11,060
Give it back to me.

441
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:13,540
That's my life's savings.

442
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,420
Give it back to me!

443
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:15,420
Give it back now.

444
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,420
From now on,

445
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:17,340
our paths are separate.

446
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:19,060
Your foot injury hasn't healed yet.

447
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:20,620
Don't add a new one.

448
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:21,860
Please, give it back.

449
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:25,220
Give it back.

450
00:18:25,860 --> 00:18:27,180
Here.

451
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:31,900
Just 30 wen.

452
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:38,660
Sorry, Sixi.

453
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:39,500
It's really

454
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:40,500
my fault.

455
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,340
I aimed too high.

456
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,340
I was too ambitious.

457
00:18:42,580 --> 00:18:44,100
And I failed to protect you.

458
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:45,780
You didn't have

459
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:46,740
to leave.

460
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:50,740
- Sixi.
- Sixi.

461
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:52,140
Sixi...

462
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:53,380
Don't follow me.

463
00:19:04,780 --> 00:19:10,500
(Jing Residence)

464
00:19:16,340 --> 00:19:17,260
Ma'am,

465
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:18,760
do you need a sedan chair?

466
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:21,620
Come on.

467
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:22,740
Take it slow.

468
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:27,300
Ma'am, where are we going?

469
00:19:27,310 --> 00:19:28,180
Leave first.

470
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,100
Alright.

471
00:19:40,490 --> 00:19:41,380
Kan, she left.

472
00:19:41,380 --> 00:19:42,660
Why didn't you stop her?

473
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:46,900
What right do I have?

474
00:20:19,540 --> 00:20:21,260
How did I end up like this?

475
00:20:22,740 --> 00:20:24,060
No money to spend,

476
00:20:24,460 --> 00:20:25,620
nowhere to go,

477
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,620
and no home to return.

478
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,340
Sixi,

479
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:11,180
I didn't mean to give him the money.

480
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:12,780
I thought you two were close.

481
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:15,340
Close my foot.

482
00:21:18,620 --> 00:21:19,980
Sixi, wipe it off.

483
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:20,980
Go away.

484
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:31,340
I think Kan is very good.

485
00:21:31,940 --> 00:21:33,580
I think he's sincere with you.

486
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:37,140
How much is sincerity worth?

487
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:39,820
It can't even get me half a bun.

488
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:45,780
Why am I so unlucky?

489
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:49,700
What were you thinking?

490
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:50,620
I don't know.

491
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:51,900
At that moment, I just gave him

492
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:52,940
the money somehow.

493
00:21:53,180 --> 00:21:55,140
I've saved it for so long,

494
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:56,740
and it's gone

495
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:57,740
in no time.

496
00:21:57,980 --> 00:21:59,420
Then why did you give it to me?

497
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:00,340
I...

498
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:04,260
Even your death won't calm my anger.

499
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:05,420
Go ahead, beat me.

500
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:11,980
It's all my fault.

501
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:15,380
(Anping Bridge)

502
00:22:15,380 --> 00:22:17,140
(Jinyu Tea)

503
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:27,740
Sir,

504
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:29,120
do you have Yunjiaojin Tea?

505
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:30,380
Sorry, no.

506
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:33,180
Isn't this Jinyu Tea?

507
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:35,500
We mainly sell Jinyu Tea,

508
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:36,420
not tea.

509
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:39,700
We have all kinds of teas,

510
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,620
except for those from Jinyu Tea.

511
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:43,220
They're all there. Pick yourself.

512
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:44,740
Forget it.

513
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:52,860
You look so down.

514
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:54,740
Who'd buy tea from you?

515
00:22:54,740 --> 00:22:55,660
Sixi.

516
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:00,540
Sixi, you...

517
00:23:02,420 --> 00:23:04,660
It's good that you're back.

518
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:05,940
Guiwei.

519
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:12,060
Your IOU.

520
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,420
Give it to me first.

521
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:16,060
I'll sign it later.

522
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,340
I still want to leave,

523
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:20,460
but you owe me money,

524
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,020
so leaving now would be a loss.

525
00:23:22,020 --> 00:23:23,660
Totally understood.

526
00:23:30,060 --> 00:23:31,260
I heard from Guiwei

527
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,920
that you borrowed money from Grandmother

528
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:33,620
to buy the tea.

529
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:36,900
Yes.

530
00:23:37,060 --> 00:23:38,500
Why didn't you borrow before?

531
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,220
I had sworn

532
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,120
never to use a cent
of the family's money.

533
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:44,660
Now, I see I was naive.

534
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:46,500
You swore never to use it,

535
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:47,540
not never to borrow.

536
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:48,420
Right.

537
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:49,380
I only realized this

538
00:23:49,380 --> 00:23:50,420
after I met you.

539
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:51,980
Sixi,

540
00:23:52,260 --> 00:23:53,540
please stay by my side

541
00:23:53,740 --> 00:23:54,700
and teach me.

542
00:24:01,380 --> 00:24:02,300
Don't give me that.

543
00:24:05,340 --> 00:24:06,620
But indeed,

544
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:08,700
Luo Wuchang controls the tea plantation

545
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:09,620
and won't give us tea.

546
00:24:09,780 --> 00:24:11,620
This shop, then, is like an empty shell.

547
00:24:12,060 --> 00:24:13,400
Half of the three-month bet period

548
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,220
has already passed.

549
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,820
If I don't go get some tea from outside,

550
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:18,020
won't that be giving up already?

551
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:19,220
Kan,

552
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:20,140
why not just

553
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:21,320
report her to the Old Lady?

554
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,540
Wouldn't that make it look

555
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,380
like I'm helpless?

556
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:24,740
Aren't you already helpless?

557
00:24:24,740 --> 00:24:25,660
Alright.

558
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:27,260
Jing Kan has a point.

559
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:29,120
So what if we report her?

560
00:24:29,460 --> 00:24:31,460
She could secretly mix in

561
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:32,380
inferior leaves.

562
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,600
We can't guard against it all.

563
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:35,380
If you ask me,

564
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,380
not getting tea
from the Jing tea plantation

565
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:38,380
is actually a good thing.

566
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:40,740
A couple thinks alike.

567
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,820
It's just running a shop.

568
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:46,260
What's so difficult?

569
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:48,340
Sixi,

570
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,980
with you here, I feel at ease.

571
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:53,420
Sixi, we'll follow your lead.

572
00:24:53,420 --> 00:24:54,620
Just tell us what to do.

573
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:55,700
What to do?

574
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:58,900
We'll start from the first step.

575
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:00,260
Okay.

576
00:25:00,740 --> 00:25:01,660
What is

577
00:25:02,660 --> 00:25:03,580
the first step?

578
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:06,660
Know our enemy.

579
00:25:15,620 --> 00:25:20,500
(Jinyu Tea Plantation)

580
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:23,460
Next month,

581
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,500
as long as each of you puts in

582
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:27,940
10% more effort than this month,

583
00:25:28,220 --> 00:25:29,660
then your income will...

584
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:30,980
Increase by 10%?

585
00:25:30,980 --> 00:25:32,820
No, it will be especially stable.

586
00:25:34,380 --> 00:25:36,020
(Sweet and Fragrant Tea)

