00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:54,780
And tastes better.

598
00:25:54,780 --> 00:25:57,700
(Jinyu Tea)
Jinyu Tea looks green and tastes better.

599
00:25:58,860 --> 00:25:59,780
Get to work.

600
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:02,980
Mr. Yu, Mr. Yu.

601
00:26:03,260 --> 00:26:04,780
Don't rush to leave yet.

602
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:05,820
Mr. Yu, Mr. Yu.

603
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:06,780
What do you want to say?

604
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:07,800
Wait.

605
00:26:08,420 --> 00:26:09,160
Mr. Yu.

606
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,110
What do you want to say?

607
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:11,060
Let's chat.

608
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:12,460
Why leave just after arriving?

609
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:13,380
Ask him.

610
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:15,300
Well, Mr. Yu wants

611
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:17,500
to buy Yunjiaojin at five qian per jin.

612
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,540
Why didn't you say how much I need?

613
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,020
Mr. Wang,

614
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:23,940
as you know,

615
00:26:24,100 --> 00:26:25,260
I used to use

616
00:26:25,260 --> 00:26:26,820
Longwochun from Laolongtan.

617
00:26:26,820 --> 00:26:28,100
Your Yunjiaojin

618
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,540
can't compare with Longwochun,

619
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:31,620
- but we're friends, right?
- Right.

620
00:26:31,620 --> 00:26:33,460
I'm here to help your business.

621
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,260
You don't even let me have five qian.

622
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:36,580
That's unfair.

623
00:26:37,220 --> 00:26:38,140
Mr. Yu.

624
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:40,860
Look, we've always sold

625
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,340
Yunjiaojin

626
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:44,220
at one tael per jin.

627
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:45,340
You offer five qian?

628
00:26:45,580 --> 00:26:47,780
You're making things hard for us.

629
00:26:48,380 --> 00:26:49,660
Just five qian per jin.

630
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:50,860
No more.

631
00:26:51,180 --> 00:26:52,740
I'll go to Laolongtan then.

632
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:53,660
Wait a moment.

633
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:55,540
Mr. Yu,

634
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:56,660
how about this?

635
00:26:57,300 --> 00:26:58,700
I can't decide

636
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,300
the price,

637
00:27:00,860 --> 00:27:02,100
but if you buy ten jin,

638
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:04,140
I'll personally give you

639
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,660
five boxes of tea snacks.

640
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,220
The festival is coming.

641
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:09,820
It's perfect

642
00:27:10,060 --> 00:27:11,740
for visiting relatives.

643
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:13,340
- Right?
- That's true.

644
00:27:13,340 --> 00:27:14,260
Besides,

645
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:15,180
our tea snacks

646
00:27:15,340 --> 00:27:16,580
aren't cheap.

647
00:27:16,580 --> 00:27:17,440
Mr. Wang,

648
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,460
you can't give them away.

649
00:27:18,460 --> 00:27:20,100
We must give them!

650
00:27:20,460 --> 00:27:21,460
Don't worry about cost.

651
00:27:21,860 --> 00:27:23,900
Go, wrap them for Mr. Yu.

652
00:27:23,900 --> 00:27:24,760
- Okay.
- Hurry.

653
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:28,660
Later,

654
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:30,540
I'll send you some

655
00:27:30,540 --> 00:27:32,220
of our newly developed tea.

656
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:33,260
You can try it first.

657
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:35,660
It can't be bought anywhere else.

658
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:37,420
Give me your feedback.

659
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:40,060
Wang,

660
00:27:40,380 --> 00:27:41,380
you are

661
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:42,740
such a good friend.

662
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:44,340
When my new tavern opens,

663
00:27:44,660 --> 00:27:45,900
I'll still use your tea.

664
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:47,450
Thank you.

665
00:27:47,450 --> 00:27:48,340
We're friends.

666
00:27:48,340 --> 00:27:49,260
Your tea snacks.

667
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:51,340
The tea snacks are good.

668
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:53,260
See you next time.

669
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:54,620
Goodbye.

670
00:27:55,180 --> 00:27:56,060
Mr. Yu, take care.

671
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:56,980
Take care.

672
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:00,100
Mr. Wang.

673
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:02,460
That batch of tea snacks
has been stored for a long time.

674
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:03,380
They might be spoiled.

675
00:28:03,460 --> 00:28:05,580
Does it say when they were made?

676
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:07,700
No.

677
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,500
Then it's fine.

678
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:15,820
(Wonton)

679
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:17,540
So, that's how tea is sold.

680
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:21,060
You said we should know our enemy.

681
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:22,900
Could it be you want

682
00:28:22,900 --> 00:28:24,420
to poach Mr. Wang?

683
00:28:25,260 --> 00:28:27,500
Sixi, we have a manager now.

684
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,740
Why poach him?

685
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:31,100
He works for Luo Zhusi.

686
00:28:31,100 --> 00:28:32,940
Poaching him would be like inviting...

687
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:34,180
A wolf into the house.

688
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,780
Exactly, that's what I mean.

689
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:37,700
I'm telling you.

690
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:38,620
This man is deceitful.

691
00:28:38,780 --> 00:28:39,700
Stay away from him.

692
00:28:40,780 --> 00:28:42,180
But on the other hand,

693
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,940
we do need a manager

694
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:45,220
who knows how to run a shop.

695
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:49,020
Kan, I can run a shop.

696
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:51,460
Indeed, talent is rare.

697
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:53,550
Isn't it running poorly now?

698
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:54,500
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

699
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,140
- I...
- The rain is getting heavier.

700
00:28:58,460 --> 00:28:59,620
I can do it, Sixi.

701
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,940
- Let me.
- You two...

702
00:29:00,940 --> 00:29:01,860
Let's go.

703
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,180
Why is the rain so heavy?

704
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,620
Wait for me, you two.

705
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:11,620
(Noodles, Anping Bridge,
Jinyu Tea Plantation)

706
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:12,540
What to eat?

707
00:29:12,820 --> 00:29:13,740
Anything is fine.

708
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,640
Sir, three bowls of noodles.

709
00:29:15,700 --> 00:29:16,620
All with eggs.

710
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:18,040
I'll have one more meatball.

711
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:18,960
Alright.

712
00:29:22,140 --> 00:29:24,140
Sixi, shall we change seats?

713
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:25,340
It's too sunny over there.

714
00:29:25,340 --> 00:29:27,140
No need, I'm fine.

715
00:29:40,540 --> 00:29:41,500
What is this?

716
00:29:51,140 --> 00:29:52,220
I was

717
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:53,380
just thinking.

718
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:55,740
If we want to run this shop well,

719
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:56,860
there are two things to do.

720
00:29:57,580 --> 00:29:59,060
First, we need to learn

721
00:29:59,060 --> 00:30:00,380
how to sell tea.

722
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:02,660
Second, we must have

723
00:30:02,660 --> 00:30:04,380
better tea than others.

724
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,020
But where can we find

725
00:30:06,020 --> 00:30:06,940
better tea?

726
00:30:07,420 --> 00:30:08,940
The tea we currently stock

727
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:10,300
is basically the kind

728
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:11,780
all tea shops in Taiping County sell.

729
00:30:12,100 --> 00:30:13,020
Good tea

730
00:30:13,020 --> 00:30:14,140
is usually sold exclusively.

731
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:16,380
We now have the Jinyu Tea sign,

732
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:18,060
so there's no chance for cooperation.

733
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,460
But we shouldn't be discouraged.

734
00:30:19,520 --> 00:30:20,580
At least we learned today

735
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:22,140
that the enemy isn't very strong.

736
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:27,020
Alright.

737
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,260
Two bowls of noodles, enjoy.

738
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:29,180
Thank you.

739
00:30:50,660 --> 00:30:54,420
(Retired and Principled)

740
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:56,800
Though we're inexperienced
in running the shop,

741
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,640
our shop is finally open.

742
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,900
We have to thank you for your support.

743
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,340
Really.

744
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:03,620
Mr. An, you truly give us

745
00:31:03,620 --> 00:31:05,020
a second life.

746
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,340
This term isn't used like that.

747
00:31:07,340 --> 00:31:08,260
It's meant that way.

748
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,060
Not calling me old man?

749
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:13,580
With your talent,

750
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:14,940
how could I call you old man?

751
00:31:15,060 --> 00:31:16,540
I'm surely not a smooth talker.

752
00:31:16,540 --> 00:31:17,460
Really.

753
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,420
Mr. An,

754
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:22,060
look at this Gongchun teapot.

755
00:31:22,500 --> 00:31:23,580
It was left by my mother.

756
00:31:23,860 --> 00:31:25,420
I heard Da Bin made it.

757
00:31:30,220 --> 00:31:31,860
In the past hundred years,

758
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:34,340
teapots were made of silver,
tin, and porcelain,

759
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:36,300
but Yixing pottery was still preferred,

760
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:38,660
because Yixing local clay

761
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,660
brings out the true fragrance of tea

762
00:31:40,980 --> 00:31:43,060
and allows tea not to spoil overnight.

763
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:46,180
As for whether it was made by Da Bin,

764
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:47,540
it's said

765
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,820
that Da Bin's teapots

766
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:52,420
are marked by a thumbprint
on the handle.

767
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,740
It really is.

768
00:32:01,940 --> 00:32:02,860
Mr. An,

769
00:32:02,860 --> 00:32:04,900
I have long admired your talent.

770
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:07,260
Though I'm average,

771
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,580
I sincerely hope

772
00:32:08,580 --> 00:32:09,660
to study with you

773
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:11,300
the art of running a tea business.

774
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,420
Mr. An, please accept me

775
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:13,820
as your disciple.

776
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:14,900
Jing Kan,

777
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:16,180
why are you so polite?

778
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:17,540
Mr. An isn't a stranger.

779
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:19,380
He was close to your mother.

780
00:32:19,380 --> 00:32:20,780
He'll definitely accept you, right?

781
00:32:20,780 --> 00:32:21,500
Hurry and kneel.

782
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,420
Yes, yes.

783
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:24,100
Sit, sit.

784
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:25,060
Have a seat.

785
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:27,140
We'll sit first.

786
00:32:27,140 --> 00:32:28,060
Alright.

787
00:32:30,980 --> 00:32:32,380
I've had

788
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,540
my final disciple.

789
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:34,780
Besides,

790
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:37,220
I don't have anything to teach you.

791
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:40,580
Mr. An, you're too modest.

792
00:32:40,580 --> 00:32:41,660
I've heard

793
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:43,460
about Jinyu Tea's first order.

794
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:44,500
You sold

795
00:32:44,650 --> 00:32:45,500
200 jin of tea

796
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:46,420
in just two hours.

797
00:32:46,620 --> 00:32:48,780
Mr. An, please help us.

798
00:32:49,020 --> 00:32:50,740
Mr. An, please.

799
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:51,900
Please.

800
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:53,700
Your teamwork

801
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:55,780
is putting me in a hard position.

802
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:56,940
Mr. An,

803
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:58,260
if you're willing to help us,

804
00:32:58,460 --> 00:32:59,900
Jing Kan will serve you diligently.

805
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:08,220
Fine.

806
00:33:09,340 --> 00:33:11,940
Sincerity can move even metal and stone.

807
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:14,620
Since you two are so sincere,

808
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:17,500
I will personally cook dinner

809
00:33:17,500 --> 00:33:18,580
for you tonight.

810
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:24,540
Dinner is good.

811
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:26,620
What about accepting Jing Kan?

812
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:28,820
- Yes.
- But I can't have

813
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:30,940
so many final disciples.

814
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,700
I can't embarrass myself.

815
00:33:33,540 --> 00:33:34,540
Is there no room

816
00:33:34,540 --> 00:33:35,460
for negotiation?

817
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:39,940
That's not entirely true.

818
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:42,780
Mencius said,

819
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:45,460
"To educate the gifted"

820
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:48,020
"is a great joy for a gentleman."

821
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:49,500
So...

822
00:33:53,460 --> 00:33:55,180
So, I can only bless you.

823
00:33:58,980 --> 00:33:59,940
Give it here.

824
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:00,860
Let's go, Jing Kan.

825
00:34:08,780 --> 00:34:09,700
If you younger ones

826
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,580
can't handle even a small setback,

827
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:13,300
how will you do great things?

828
00:34:14,980 --> 00:34:15,900
This is just

829
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:18,260
a small test for you.

830
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,160
- A test.
- A test.

831
00:34:21,170 --> 00:34:22,740
Sit, sit.

832
00:34:22,740 --> 00:34:23,660
I know, I know.

833
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:25,780
Unfortunately, you didn't pass.

834
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:27,540
Forget about being

835
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:28,860
my disciple.

836
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:30,860
Let's go.

837
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:33,740
Don't look back, go.

838
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:35,860
Wait.

839
00:34:37,860 --> 00:34:40,140
Old man, I'll trust you one last time.

840
00:34:40,140 --> 00:34:41,060
Leave the teapot.

841
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:42,780
I can help you.

842
00:34:43,940 --> 00:34:44,860
How?

843
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:50,340
My final disciple

844
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:51,980
can help you.

845
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:52,900
Go find him.

846
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,500
Give it to me.

847
00:34:54,740 --> 00:34:55,660
That's true.

848
00:34:55,660 --> 00:34:57,140
His name is Ruan Ling.

849
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:58,980
Very clever.

850
00:34:58,980 --> 00:34:59,900
Trust me.

851
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:04,640
Trust him one more time.

852
00:35:17,220 --> 00:35:19,340
At the end of the alley, the black gate.

853
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:20,340
This should be it.

854
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:28,860
Who's there?

855
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,460
Coming.

856
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:32,260
This voice sounds

857
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,580
a bit familiar.

858
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:35,380
You are...

859
00:35:35,940 --> 00:35:36,940
Sorry to disturb you...

860
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:37,860
It's you?

861
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:42,220
(Ruan Ling, Mr. An's final disciple)

862
00:35:42,580 --> 00:35:43,580
What do you mean?

863
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:45,420
He pretended

864
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:47,260
to be the Tea Master
and scammed me for money.

865
00:35:47,580 --> 00:35:48,060
Sir,

866
00:35:48,060 --> 00:35:49,760
you must've mistaken me
for someone else.

867
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:51,180
We've never met.

868
00:35:51,180 --> 00:35:52,260
We've never met?

869
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:53,680
Wasn't it you who whisked tea

870
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:54,700
at Yinyu Alley last time?

871
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:56,140
Yinyu Alley?

872
00:35:59,860 --> 00:36:00,780
I understand.

873
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:02,180
Seems there's another victim.

874
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,460
I am that victim.

875
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:04,660
Don't get worked up.

